WEBVTT

01:02.699 --> 01:05.766
<i>Life, extraordinary,</i>

01:09.035 --> 01:10.144
<i>people.</i>

01:11.345 --> 01:14.841
<i>I can't say why</i>

01:14.876 --> 01:17.613
<i>people fascinate me</i>
<i>so much.</i>

01:18.847 --> 01:20.385
<i>If I had to give a reason,</i>

01:21.784 --> 01:23.454
<i>it's because</i>

01:23.489 --> 01:25.852
<i>we're so different,</i>

01:25.887 --> 01:28.822
<i>each and every one of us.</i>

01:31.728 --> 01:33.365
<i>Isn't it amazing to know</i>

01:34.632 --> 01:36.335
<i>there's not another version</i>
<i>of you?</i>

01:37.701 --> 01:39.030
<i>There was only you.</i>

01:43.069 --> 01:45.410
<i>That's what's fascinating,</i>

01:47.744 --> 01:50.041
<i>especially women.</i>

01:55.081 --> 01:58.654
<i>What do these images</i>
<i>remind you of?</i>

02:03.694 --> 02:05.958
<i>Women.</i>

02:05.993 --> 02:09.533
<i>So complex, but so perfect.</i>

02:11.537 --> 02:14.505
<i>To understand them is like</i>
<i>trying to understand income tax.</i>

02:16.168 --> 02:17.871
<i>Exactly.</i>

02:17.906 --> 02:21.072
<i>No one gets it, but I do.</i>

02:22.207 --> 02:24.174
<i>Not income tax,</i>

02:24.209 --> 02:26.385
<i>women.</i>

02:26.420 --> 02:28.585
<i>Her, for example.</i>

02:29.885 --> 02:32.116
<i>Just look at her.</i>

02:35.264 --> 02:37.198
<i>Look how perfect she is.</i>

02:38.894 --> 02:40.927
<i>It's like</i>
<i>she was designed by Apple.</i>

02:42.535 --> 02:45.965
<i>Is she happy with him</i>
<i>in this moment?</i>

02:50.202 --> 02:53.478
<i>She's smiling,</i>
<i>but looking closely,</i>

02:54.613 --> 02:57.108
<i>her eyes,</i>

02:57.143 --> 02:58.780
<i>there's uncertainty.</i>

03:00.146 --> 03:01.651
<i>She doesn't fully trust him.</i>

03:03.248 --> 03:05.721
<i>Every time he speaks,</i>
<i>she lifts her head</i>

03:05.756 --> 03:07.085
<i>and squints her eyes.</i>

03:08.495 --> 03:10.528
<i>This could also mean</i>
<i>she's intrigued by him,</i>

03:10.563 --> 03:12.827
<i>but it's not the case here.</i>

03:14.468 --> 03:17.062
<i>This woman, for example,</i>

03:17.097 --> 03:19.504
<i>this is what intrigue</i>
<i>looks like.</i>

03:21.475 --> 03:23.574
<i>The difference is that</i>
<i>after she raises her head</i>

03:23.609 --> 03:25.807
<i>and squints her eyes,</i>

03:25.842 --> 03:28.073
<i>there's a slight adjustment</i>
<i>to her head.</i>

03:28.108 --> 03:30.977
<i>She brings it back down</i>
<i>only a little bit.</i>

03:32.277 --> 03:33.782
<i>This.</i>

03:33.817 --> 03:35.718
<i>This tells us</i>
<i>she's not only intrigued,</i>

03:35.753 --> 03:37.786
<i>but wants something.</i>

03:38.954 --> 03:40.954
<i>What does she want?</i>

03:40.989 --> 03:42.956
<i>With silence,</i>

03:42.991 --> 03:44.925
<i>I get answers.</i>

03:44.960 --> 03:47.598
<i>Silence says many things</i>

03:47.633 --> 03:49.028
<i>without saying anything.</i>

03:50.262 --> 03:52.130
<i>Next comes...</i>

03:52.165 --> 03:54.308
Why are you looking at me
like that?

03:54.343 --> 03:55.474
I'm just looking.

03:56.642 --> 03:57.839
Anything new?

03:59.480 --> 04:00.743
Few things.

04:00.778 --> 04:02.140
Like?

04:02.175 --> 04:03.779
Your perfume.

04:03.814 --> 04:04.912
That's new.

04:04.947 --> 04:06.353
Stop deflecting.

04:06.388 --> 04:07.552
You know what I'm talking
about with you.

04:08.819 --> 04:11.116
<i>It's all over her face.</i>

04:11.151 --> 04:12.854
<i>She wants me,</i>

04:14.462 --> 04:15.626
<i>and she's looking forward</i>
<i>to the day</i>

04:15.661 --> 04:17.023
<i>when it finally happens.</i>

04:19.566 --> 04:20.895
<i>But I want something else.</i>

04:24.802 --> 04:26.098
You know what?

04:26.133 --> 04:27.473
I'm, uh,
I'm getting a little tired.

04:27.508 --> 04:29.167
I think
I'm gonna call it a night.

04:29.202 --> 04:30.707
- Okay,
I'll walk you out.

04:30.742 --> 04:32.170
No, no, no, I'm good.

04:32.205 --> 04:33.347
Thank you.

04:33.382 --> 04:34.480
Have a good night.

04:34.515 --> 04:35.745
You, too.

04:37.716 --> 04:39.881
- ...wine, champagne
or whatever you want.

04:41.753 --> 04:43.181
<i>There are people</i>
<i>in this world</i>

04:43.216 --> 04:45.216
<i>who ignore</i>
<i>their natural instincts,</i>

04:46.659 --> 04:49.396
<i>our instincts of wanting more.</i>

04:51.158 --> 04:53.158
<i>In Las Vegas,</i>
<i>people tend to let go</i>

04:53.193 --> 04:56.403
<i>and live almost carefree,</i>

04:56.438 --> 04:58.867
<i>which is why I fit in so well.</i>

05:00.673 --> 05:03.003
<i>I can fulfill</i>
<i>my darkest desires,</i>

05:03.038 --> 05:05.841
<i>and no one will even notice.</i>

05:21.221 --> 05:23.254
<i>I promise,</i>
<i>it isn't what it looks like.</i>

06:20.621 --> 06:21.686
<i>Perfect.</i>

06:33.997 --> 06:35.161
Okay, okay, okay.

06:37.803 --> 06:38.967
Come on.

06:46.042 --> 06:47.514
I'm just gonna go
freshen up, okay?

07:36.191 --> 07:37.498
<i>Damn!</i>

07:38.831 --> 07:40.193
<i>What was I thinking?</i>

07:42.703 --> 07:44.230
<i>This shouldn't have happened.</i>

07:48.071 --> 07:49.576
<i>Couldn't help myself.</i>

08:02.921 --> 08:04.591
<i>What are you doing?</i>

08:20.565 --> 08:21.740
- Wait.

08:23.744 --> 08:25.172
- What are you doing?

08:25.207 --> 08:27.042
Go away!

08:27.077 --> 08:28.714
I was going to ask you
the same thing.

08:30.146 --> 08:31.475
You don't want to be here.

08:33.050 --> 08:34.951
You're right.

08:34.986 --> 08:36.854
I don't.

08:36.889 --> 08:38.086
You should leave.

08:39.485 --> 08:40.825
I think we both should.

08:44.127 --> 08:45.390
Leave or I'll jump.

08:47.592 --> 08:49.493
I'm sure you don't want
to be here anymore than I do.

08:53.774 --> 08:55.103
Don't be so sure.

08:56.909 --> 08:59.437
I'm sure that
wherever you were, you,

08:59.472 --> 09:00.812
uh, you left in a bit of a rush.

09:00.847 --> 09:04.409
You don't have a jacket,
got no purse.

09:06.985 --> 09:08.512
-Why don't we just-
-Don't!

09:10.791 --> 09:11.955
Okay.

09:13.695 --> 09:16.355
All I'm saying is,
you're not alone.

09:18.194 --> 09:20.799
Now that you have
a moment, just...

09:20.834 --> 09:22.295
just think about
what you're doing.

09:26.972 --> 09:28.741
I'm...

09:28.776 --> 09:30.534
I'm sorry about this,
I have to, I have to take this.

09:31.944 --> 09:33.603
Hello.

09:33.638 --> 09:35.308
Hey, Mama.
You okay?

09:36.784 --> 09:38.685
Okay, great. Let me, let me
give you a call back, okay?

09:40.612 --> 09:41.853
Because I'm with a friend
and I,

09:41.888 --> 09:43.052
and I don't want to be rude.

09:44.990 --> 09:46.057
With who?

09:49.126 --> 09:50.125
Emma.

09:50.160 --> 09:51.995
Emma.

09:52.030 --> 09:53.832
I'm with Emma, Ma.

09:55.627 --> 09:58.364
No, we actually, uh,
we just met. Listen, I'm...

09:58.399 --> 10:00.003
I'm trying to help her
with something right now.

10:00.038 --> 10:01.400
I'mma give you
a call back, okay?

10:02.843 --> 10:05.041
Okay.
I love you, too.

10:05.076 --> 10:06.174
All right.

10:07.408 --> 10:08.847
I'm sorry about that.

10:08.882 --> 10:10.178
If, if it wasn't my mama,

10:10.213 --> 10:12.015
I wouldn't have picked up
right now.

10:13.678 --> 10:16.118
Um...

10:16.153 --> 10:18.054
Emma, is it possible
that we can maybe

10:18.089 --> 10:19.891
go somewhere and, and talk?

10:23.325 --> 10:25.666
<i>I pay attention to things</i>
<i>most people don't see,</i>

10:27.560 --> 10:30.132
<i>but I see you, Emma.</i>

10:30.167 --> 10:32.398
<i>I treat her place</i>
<i>as if it's my own</i>

10:32.433 --> 10:33.872
<i>to make her more comfortable.</i>

10:35.106 --> 10:37.040
Uh, where's your light?

10:37.075 --> 10:38.745
-Over here.
-Okay.

10:40.342 --> 10:41.407
Leave it.

10:43.510 --> 10:44.817
Okay.

10:44.852 --> 10:46.984
I'mma go grab you
some blankets

10:47.019 --> 10:48.678
or something, okay?

10:48.713 --> 10:51.186
And we can talk about
whatever you want to talk about.

10:54.961 --> 10:56.092
It's okay.

10:57.623 --> 11:00.228
We all go through things, okay?

11:00.263 --> 11:01.328
I've been there.

11:01.363 --> 11:02.428
We all have.

11:10.141 --> 11:12.042
<i>I'm not taking</i>
<i>advantage of this woman.</i>

11:16.378 --> 11:17.718
<i>This isn't for me.</i>

11:22.582 --> 11:24.120
<i>This is for her.</i>

11:28.720 --> 11:30.588
<i>Believe it or not,</i>
<i>she needs this.</i>

11:33.593 --> 11:34.801
<i>She's broken.</i>

11:39.104 --> 11:41.005
<i>And I'm her temporary fix,</i>

11:45.946 --> 11:47.176
<i>just a moment,</i>

11:51.952 --> 11:53.446
<i>a feeling...</i>

11:57.925 --> 11:59.584
<i>she wishes can last forever.</i>

12:28.351 --> 12:31.924
<i>Last night was definitely</i>
<i>an unusual night for me.</i>

12:31.959 --> 12:33.354
<i>But what happened, happened</i>

12:33.389 --> 12:34.718
<i>so I can be there for her.</i>

12:40.396 --> 12:43.804
<i>"Emma, I'm sorry I had to leave.</i>

12:45.368 --> 12:47.808
<i>"You looked so comfortable</i>
<i>and I didn't want to wake you.</i>

12:49.207 --> 12:51.845
<i>"What a night we shared.</i>

12:51.880 --> 12:55.013
<i>"It feels as if it was meant</i>
<i>to be because</i>

12:55.048 --> 12:57.609
<i>"we both needed someone.</i>

12:57.644 --> 12:59.380
<i>"Thank you for being</i>
<i>there for me.</i>

13:00.988 --> 13:02.823
<i>"Stop reading and look</i>
<i>under your pillow.</i>

13:04.816 --> 13:08.653
<i>"Don't think of this as charity</i>
<i>or anything like that.</i>

13:08.688 --> 13:12.525
<i>"Look at it as a thank you</i>
<i>for an experience</i>

13:12.560 --> 13:13.834
<i>"that was priceless.</i>

13:15.101 --> 13:17.431
<i>"It's not much,</i>
<i>but I hope this helps.</i>

13:18.907 --> 13:20.236
<i>"You take care of yourself."</i>

13:25.276 --> 13:26.880
<i>Money,</i>

13:26.915 --> 13:29.344
<i>the root of all evil,</i>

13:29.379 --> 13:30.741
<i>almost made us loser.</i>

13:32.085 --> 13:34.745
<i>Money is never my go-to,</i>

13:34.780 --> 13:37.682
<i>but in this case,</i>
<i>it was necessary.</i>

13:37.717 --> 13:40.025
<i>It possibly saved her life.</i>

13:40.060 --> 13:42.060
<i>I'll never know.</i>

13:42.095 --> 13:43.226
<i>It's best that way.</i>

13:44.559 --> 13:46.658
<i>I live in the moment.</i>

13:46.693 --> 13:48.726
<i>Last night we had a moment.</i>

13:50.268 --> 13:53.698
<i>Now that moment is over,</i>
<i>it's time to move on.</i>

14:12.620 --> 14:14.521
What up, boss?
You in early.

14:14.556 --> 14:16.094
And you're late.

14:16.129 --> 14:17.689
I'm not sure
if you noticed me over

14:17.724 --> 14:18.899
in the lobby, sir,
but I was here before you.

14:20.496 --> 14:22.364
What time do we open?

14:22.399 --> 14:23.794
At- 00.

14:23.829 --> 14:25.136
What time is it now?

14:26.766 --> 14:27.941
- 50.

14:27.976 --> 14:29.206
Who do you work for?

14:29.241 --> 14:30.867
For you, sir.

14:30.902 --> 14:32.077
But I'm not really
understanding these questions.

14:32.112 --> 14:33.243
You work for me?

14:33.278 --> 14:35.707
Is my office in the lobby?

14:37.414 --> 14:40.954
If you're not at your desk
at- 45, you're late.

14:40.989 --> 14:42.384
How are you assisting me

14:42.419 --> 14:43.418
when there's no assistant
for my client

14:43.453 --> 14:44.617
when they come in, Kevin?

14:47.754 --> 14:49.259
I need you to be
more professional here.

14:51.131 --> 14:54.297
You represent me,
so I need you to represent.

14:55.762 --> 14:57.267
Talk to the ladies
on your break.

14:57.302 --> 14:58.631
Matter of fact, give them
a chance to come to you.

15:00.701 --> 15:02.569
But, Joe, did you see shorty?

15:02.604 --> 15:04.109
She was bad as hell.

15:04.144 --> 15:05.440
You can't wait
on a piece of ass like that.

15:05.475 --> 15:07.178
You feel me?
You've seen it.

15:12.383 --> 15:14.680
<i>There's</i>
<i>no re-living moments.</i>

15:14.715 --> 15:18.552
<i>Trust me,</i>
<i>it never turns out well.</i>

15:31.336 --> 15:32.467
- There he is.

15:33.965 --> 15:35.305
Another great night, huh?

15:36.539 --> 15:39.210
I take it you had
another bad one.

15:39.245 --> 15:40.541
Don't want to talk about it.

15:41.874 --> 15:44.941
I just-I don't understand.

15:44.976 --> 15:47.779
You're very handsome
and intelligent, man.

15:47.814 --> 15:49.022
You would think
after all this time,

15:49.057 --> 15:50.188
she'd recognize it.

15:50.223 --> 15:51.420
Yeah, you would think.

15:53.820 --> 15:55.193
Just give it
another 10 years or so.

15:55.228 --> 15:57.195
I don't have 10 years!

15:59.430 --> 16:00.660
I'm just joking, man.

16:02.169 --> 16:03.333
I have an idea.

16:04.567 --> 16:06.567
I'm not cheating on my wife.

16:06.602 --> 16:08.866
I'm not suggesting you
cheat on your wife.

16:10.375 --> 16:11.440
What?

16:14.577 --> 16:18.315
What I was going
to suggest is, for today,

16:18.350 --> 16:21.153
we switch assistants,

16:21.188 --> 16:22.781
help make your day
a little easier.

16:27.458 --> 16:31.196
Malcolm, we've known
each other a long time.

16:31.231 --> 16:33.363
16 strong years.

16:33.398 --> 16:35.167
Yeah.

16:35.202 --> 16:36.894
And you don't think
I wouldn't recognize

16:36.929 --> 16:38.170
when you're trying
to manipulate me?

16:39.932 --> 16:41.404
Kevin is horrible.

16:41.439 --> 16:42.702
-Kevin is not that bad.
-You know what?

16:44.035 --> 16:45.573
You can have Melissa
for the day.

16:45.608 --> 16:47.113
Thank you.

16:47.148 --> 16:49.280
But we get to switch offices
for the week.

16:49.315 --> 16:50.776
-How does that even-
-I didn't think so.

16:52.549 --> 16:54.186
Why do you get
the best office anyway?

16:54.221 --> 16:55.517
We're supposed to be partners.

16:55.552 --> 16:56.617
We are-

16:57.752 --> 16:59.620
We are partners.

16:59.655 --> 17:01.325
I pay more rent than you do.

17:07.927 --> 17:09.795
<i>I remember</i>
<i>when Calvin first got married.</i>

17:11.997 --> 17:15.438
<i>They were happy for a moment.</i>

17:19.576 --> 17:24.150
<i>The thing is,</i>
<i>love doesn't exist,</i>

17:25.681 --> 17:27.285
<i>only lustful moments.</i>

17:28.783 --> 17:30.453
<i>When we have a moment</i>
<i>with someone,</i>

17:32.160 --> 17:34.985
<i>we try to extend this moment</i>
<i>to last longer than intended.</i>

17:38.298 --> 17:40.023
<i>That's how relationships happen.</i>

17:43.028 --> 17:47.107
<i>And you end up here...</i>
<i>seeking counsel.</i>

17:54.776 --> 17:56.347
- Sir, uh,
your 9 o'clock is here.

17:56.382 --> 17:57.480
Send her in.

18:00.947 --> 18:02.683
Hello, Mr. King.

18:02.718 --> 18:05.620
Elizabeth, I told you,
call me Malcolm.

18:05.655 --> 18:07.358
And I told you to call me Liz.

18:10.154 --> 18:11.527
How you doing?

18:11.562 --> 18:13.529
I'm actually doing good.

18:13.564 --> 18:15.663
Things are good, thanks to you.

18:15.698 --> 18:17.830
-Nice.
-Yeah.

18:17.865 --> 18:19.172
-Take a seat.
-Thanks.

18:22.969 --> 18:26.135
So I finally convinced
my husband to come in.

18:26.170 --> 18:28.137
-Really?
-Yeah.

18:28.172 --> 18:29.347
Wow.
How did you do that?

18:29.382 --> 18:30.975
It wasn't easy.

18:31.010 --> 18:32.680
I bet.

18:32.715 --> 18:34.044
So then he'll be joining us
in your next session?

18:34.079 --> 18:36.189
No, he's actually here now.

18:36.224 --> 18:37.190
Listen, I understand.

18:37.225 --> 18:38.521
I got to go.

18:38.556 --> 18:40.655
Uh-Hey, sorry.
Work.

18:40.690 --> 18:42.657
<i>Work, huh?</i>
<i>That's original.</i>

18:42.692 --> 18:44.230
I had to take it.

18:44.265 --> 18:48.564
Um, Mr. King-Malcolm,
this is my husband, Zach.

18:48.599 --> 18:51.061
You look familiar.
Have we met before?

18:55.672 --> 18:57.210
I'm sure I'd remember.

18:57.245 --> 18:58.409
Of course.

19:00.039 --> 19:02.809
Nice to finally meet you,
Zach, I've heard so much.

19:02.844 --> 19:04.514
I hope not all bad.

19:04.549 --> 19:05.713
<i>Of course it is.</i>

19:05.748 --> 19:07.143
Please, take a seat.

19:07.178 --> 19:08.254
Thank you.

19:12.458 --> 19:15.690
So, Zach, I want you
to tell me

19:15.725 --> 19:17.527
what finally made you
decide to come in?

19:18.860 --> 19:20.332
Well, you just get
right to it, huh?

19:20.367 --> 19:21.564
Well, you are paying
by the hour, so...

19:22.897 --> 19:24.028
Honestly...

19:26.736 --> 19:28.131
I love my wife, Malcolm-

19:29.233 --> 19:30.375
Mr. King.

19:33.413 --> 19:35.941
Mr. King,

19:35.976 --> 19:38.009
I want things to work.

19:38.044 --> 19:39.780
I know my wife feels
very strongly about me

19:39.815 --> 19:41.254
coming in to see you.

19:41.289 --> 19:43.883
And here I am, so...

19:45.293 --> 19:47.293
I understand there's
ups and downs in relationships,

19:47.328 --> 19:49.185
we have them,
everyone has them,

19:49.220 --> 19:50.560
you know, but that's
the whole reason

19:50.595 --> 19:51.462
we got married
in the first place.

19:51.497 --> 19:53.024
We love each other.

19:53.059 --> 19:54.795
You know, I think
there's just about anything-

19:54.830 --> 19:57.897
<i>This is what bothers</i>
<i>me the most about my job.</i>

19:57.932 --> 20:03.408
<i>There's so much hope</i>
<i>in her eyes, the pain she's in.</i>

20:03.443 --> 20:04.772
<i>Just hang in there, Liz.</i>

20:15.587 --> 20:17.950
Melissa.

20:17.985 --> 20:20.260
Is any of these clients
here for us?

20:21.494 --> 20:22.988
If you actually did your job,

20:23.023 --> 20:24.759
you wouldn't have
to ask me that.

20:26.290 --> 20:29.060
Well, the thing is, though,

20:29.095 --> 20:31.370
everybody here looks old
and miserable, I guess not.

20:37.268 --> 20:39.103
Hmm, hmm, hmm, hmm.

20:41.041 --> 20:42.975
What are you staring at?

20:43.010 --> 20:44.284
Staring at you, beautiful.

20:46.046 --> 20:47.287
Well, stop.

20:48.488 --> 20:50.620
Stop?

20:50.655 --> 20:52.325
I think it's time
we stop playing these games

20:52.360 --> 20:54.954
with each other and really say
what's on our minds.

20:57.662 --> 20:59.156
What the fuck
are you talking about?

20:59.191 --> 21:00.300
- Hmm.

21:01.963 --> 21:03.963
No, no. No!

21:03.998 --> 21:05.096
Let him go.

21:05.131 --> 21:06.570
It's about us.

21:08.332 --> 21:09.474
Oh, my God.

21:11.236 --> 21:13.379
Well, that concludes
our session.

21:15.680 --> 21:16.745
I'll walk you guys out.

21:24.392 --> 21:25.622
Thank you.

21:25.657 --> 21:26.656
Thank you.
I'll see you soon.

21:26.691 --> 21:27.756
I'll see you soon.

21:29.221 --> 21:34.631
Like I said, I'm all in,
Mal-Mr. King.

21:34.666 --> 21:37.997
Thank you for being
there for her, for us.

21:38.032 --> 21:39.636
What happened here?

21:39.671 --> 21:41.407
Oh, um, nothing.

21:41.442 --> 21:42.771
-Work stuff.
-Hmm.

21:45.006 --> 21:46.478
Thank you for coming in, Zach.

21:46.513 --> 21:47.644
Yeah.

21:47.679 --> 21:48.744
See you soon.

21:51.419 --> 21:52.847
<i>Zach thinks he has me</i>
<i>convinced</i>

21:52.882 --> 21:54.178
<i>he cares about his marriage.</i>

21:57.282 --> 21:59.051
<i>The only thing</i>
<i>you convinced me</i>

21:59.086 --> 22:00.723
<i>of is that you truly care</i>
<i>about your mistress.</i>

22:06.027 --> 22:07.400
What is this?

22:25.948 --> 22:27.882
<i>You want to convince</i>
<i>your wife enough</i>

22:27.917 --> 22:29.719
<i>so you can continue</i>
<i>to get away with it.</i>

22:33.120 --> 22:35.428
<i>Too bad your mistress</i>
<i>doesn't feel the same about you.</i>

23:55.741 --> 23:57.037
I've heard about you.

23:59.844 --> 24:01.008
The Messiah.

24:03.507 --> 24:04.682
<i>Who?</i>

24:15.662 --> 24:18.322
So you are the savior of women?

24:18.357 --> 24:19.565
<i>She's not scared.</i>

24:20.931 --> 24:22.997
<i>In fact, she looks</i>
<i>almost happy to see me.</i>

24:24.495 --> 24:26.198
<i>A strange man</i>
<i>in your house with a mask</i>

24:26.233 --> 24:27.672
<i>and you're okay with it?</i>

24:29.005 --> 24:30.070
Nothing to say?

24:31.678 --> 24:33.073
<i>You'll tell me</i>
<i>what I want to know.</i>

24:36.947 --> 24:39.409
No, I think it's beautiful
what you're doing,

24:41.413 --> 24:43.248
showing these women
who they married.

24:53.700 --> 24:55.194
I've been wanting to meet you.

24:57.704 --> 24:59.033
For the longest,

24:59.068 --> 25:00.771
I wasn't even sure
if you existed.

25:04.810 --> 25:06.436
We share a common interest,

25:10.981 --> 25:12.376
as you already know.

25:13.951 --> 25:15.918
<i>She knows</i>
<i>what she's doing,</i>

25:15.953 --> 25:18.184
<i>talking,</i>
<i>but not saying anything.</i>

25:18.219 --> 25:19.218
Sure?

25:19.253 --> 25:20.516
<i>She's smart.</i>

25:20.551 --> 25:21.627
It's good.

25:23.488 --> 25:24.597
Raincheck.

25:26.326 --> 25:28.293
<i>Why is this woman not scared?</i>

25:30.165 --> 25:31.967
So, how did you find me?

25:33.300 --> 25:34.398
- You?

25:37.502 --> 25:40.580
Wait, you're not here for me?

25:44.014 --> 25:45.046
I thought...

25:48.656 --> 25:50.480
Wow.

25:50.515 --> 25:51.954
- I should leave.

25:55.091 --> 25:56.156
Wait.

25:57.830 --> 26:00.325
Is it only married
women you save?

26:03.363 --> 26:04.703
I guess so.

26:28.619 --> 26:30.553
- So,
how much do you know?

26:34.966 --> 26:36.064
What?

26:44.877 --> 26:46.140
You wanna take pictures...

26:50.014 --> 26:51.079
For the wife?

26:56.218 --> 26:57.415
You deserve it.

27:00.387 --> 27:01.518
But what about me?

27:03.830 --> 27:04.928
What do I get?

27:07.262 --> 27:08.701
The heartbroken mistress?

27:14.038 --> 27:17.039
I'll do it for you.

27:19.879 --> 27:21.373
But I want something in return.

28:36.615 --> 28:37.856
It's my sister.

28:49.529 --> 28:50.770
<i>How do you know me?</i>

28:52.532 --> 28:56.336
<i>If you knew my name,</i>
<i>you would have said it.</i>

28:59.704 --> 29:01.671
<i>And why would you think</i>
<i>I was there for you?</i>

29:05.149 --> 29:06.610
<i>It's been over a week,</i>

29:06.645 --> 29:07.886
<i>and I can't get you</i>
<i>out of my mind.</i>

29:11.617 --> 29:15.685
<i>We had a moment,</i>
<i>but that moment has passed.</i>

29:18.899 --> 29:20.129
<i>Move on, Malcolm.</i>

29:25.499 --> 29:29.138
<i>Sometimes,</i>
<i>it's difficult to let go.</i>

29:33.243 --> 29:34.539
<i>So I look at these...</i>

29:39.711 --> 29:41.744
<i>to remind me of what once was.</i>

31:49.874 --> 31:51.016
<i>- You like my hair?</i>

31:51.051 --> 31:52.413
<i>Yeah?</i>

31:54.054 --> 31:55.812
<i>- This is always</i>
<i>the hardest part.</i>

31:55.847 --> 31:57.748
<i>- I appreciate it.</i>

31:57.783 --> 32:00.025
<i>- I had to wait</i>
<i>until she had time to process.</i>

32:02.623 --> 32:04.359
<i>While Zach</i>
<i>was on his business trip</i>

32:04.394 --> 32:06.526
<i>for a few days</i>
<i>it was the perfect time.</i>

32:08.662 --> 32:09.969
<i>I'm sorry, Liz.</i>

32:11.863 --> 32:16.503
<i>Love, the word shouldn't exist.</i>

32:16.538 --> 32:20.408
<i>It should be replaced with pain</i>
<i>because that's how love is.</i>

32:23.809 --> 32:25.017
What's going on, man?

32:27.318 --> 32:28.911
Just don't know
how much longer I can take this.

32:30.684 --> 32:33.751
You know, you say that a lot,
but yet you still do.

32:35.018 --> 32:36.853
I want my family.

32:36.888 --> 32:38.657
After 10 years, marriage,

32:38.692 --> 32:41.462
raising kids
and family vacations, it's...

32:43.664 --> 32:45.301
It's not like
you understand, right?

32:45.336 --> 32:47.006
What do you mean, man?
I get it.

32:48.240 --> 32:49.833
Sorry. I just...

32:49.868 --> 32:51.307
It's cool.

32:51.342 --> 32:52.440
I just...

32:54.114 --> 32:56.114
wish my wife wanted me,
you know?

32:57.678 --> 32:59.381
Everything I do
is a failed attempt.

33:06.016 --> 33:07.488
What happened?

33:12.462 --> 33:13.560
- Hmm.

33:14.794 --> 33:16.563
So tired.

33:18.897 --> 33:19.896
Goodnight, honey.

33:19.931 --> 33:21.337
Goodnight?

33:21.372 --> 33:22.602
I'm tired.

33:27.070 --> 33:28.773
Mm-mmm.

33:28.808 --> 33:30.511
Hey.

33:33.153 --> 33:34.284
Oh.

33:37.949 --> 33:42.292
Oh, baby, what's wrong?

33:42.327 --> 33:43.689
I'm scared.

33:43.724 --> 33:46.956
Oh, honey,
did you have a bad dream?

33:46.991 --> 33:48.727
You need to sleep
with mommy and daddy?

33:48.762 --> 33:50.729
-Mm-hmm.
-Well, come here.

33:50.764 --> 33:52.401
Come here.

33:52.436 --> 33:53.666
Oh, let's put you up.

33:55.065 --> 33:56.702
-Oh!
-All right.

33:56.737 --> 33:58.539
You want covers?

33:58.574 --> 34:00.607
Oh, that's my girl.

34:00.642 --> 34:02.114
Mmm, is that better?

34:02.149 --> 34:03.247
She just went to bed
10 minutes ago.

34:03.282 --> 34:04.479
Shh!

35:18.885 --> 35:20.049
Oh, my God!

35:20.084 --> 35:21.226
Oh!

35:24.759 --> 35:26.154
Why didn't you lock the door?

35:26.189 --> 35:27.529
There's no lock on it.

35:27.564 --> 35:29.201
So you don't do it then?

35:29.236 --> 35:30.730
You don't understand,
it's been like six months.

35:30.765 --> 35:32.303
-Six months, man.
-Yeah.

35:32.338 --> 35:33.865
That's crazy.

35:35.737 --> 35:37.132
-Good morning.
-How'd you sleep?

35:37.167 --> 35:38.375
Really well.

35:38.410 --> 35:39.706
-Yeah?
-Mm-hmm.

35:40.940 --> 35:42.005
Wow.
Man, that's-

35:42.040 --> 35:43.248
Is that for me?

35:43.283 --> 35:44.414
Oh, yeah, you can take this.

35:44.449 --> 35:45.547
Thank you.

35:48.046 --> 35:50.046
I'll, uh,
I'll be in there in a minute.

35:50.081 --> 35:51.223
You better.

35:55.020 --> 35:56.228
Wow.

35:56.263 --> 35:57.361
Six months, huh?

35:58.925 --> 36:00.188
Yeah, that's crazy, man.

36:00.223 --> 36:01.497
I'm sorry about that.

36:01.532 --> 36:03.532
Yeah.

36:03.567 --> 36:04.797
Well, you'll see.

36:06.273 --> 36:07.635
See how it is,
when you get married.

36:09.441 --> 36:10.935
That's the thing.
I'm not-

36:10.970 --> 36:12.376
You're not getting married.
Yeah, I know.

36:12.411 --> 36:13.542
Don't.

36:17.548 --> 36:19.845
Out of all the women
you've been with,

36:19.880 --> 36:21.110
not one you actually care about?

36:22.982 --> 36:24.047
What you mean, man?

36:24.082 --> 36:25.587
I care about all of them.

36:25.622 --> 36:26.819
You know what I mean.

36:28.427 --> 36:31.494
There's actually one woman
I met recently.

36:34.257 --> 36:35.399
She's pretty interesting.

36:38.096 --> 36:40.635
Interesting, you mean,
interesting enough to see again?

36:40.670 --> 36:42.538
Exactly.

36:42.573 --> 36:43.737
Okay.

36:43.772 --> 36:45.101
So why don't you?

36:45.136 --> 36:47.543
Was it just a one-night stand?

36:47.578 --> 36:48.643
Come on, man.

36:49.910 --> 36:50.975
You know me.

36:52.616 --> 36:54.715
You know you could
try being normal for once,

36:54.750 --> 36:57.586
like, maybe even learn
the name first.

36:57.621 --> 36:59.588
You know, it's not that weird.

36:59.623 --> 37:01.249
Do me a favor, man.
I'm about to take off.

37:01.284 --> 37:03.526
Can you, uh, lock up for me

37:04.991 --> 37:07.156
and then make sure
she's gone before you leave?

37:07.191 --> 37:08.432
-Appreciate you.
-What?

37:08.467 --> 37:10.258
Thanks, man.

37:10.293 --> 37:11.765
In one ear and out the other.

37:15.474 --> 37:16.902
Who am I giving advice?

37:16.937 --> 37:18.035
I can't even get laid
by my own wife.

37:25.715 --> 37:26.846
Oh, shit.

37:26.881 --> 37:28.210
All right, lady, time to go.

37:31.952 --> 37:34.216
<i>I keep coming here</i>
<i>thinking I may run into you.</i>

37:35.989 --> 37:38.924
<i>If I did, what would I even say?</i>

37:38.959 --> 37:40.189
<i>"Remember that night</i>
<i>you found out</i>

37:40.224 --> 37:41.861
<i>"your boyfriend was married?</i>

37:41.896 --> 37:43.368
<i>"I'm the guy you kissed.</i>

37:43.403 --> 37:44.600
<i>"Yeah, you know</i>
<i>the one with the mask."</i>

37:44.635 --> 37:46.404
<i>What is wrong with you, Malcolm?</i>

37:47.704 --> 37:49.770
<i>Why are you even here?</i>

37:49.805 --> 37:51.508
<i>The moment is gone, accept it.</i>

37:57.483 --> 37:58.548
<i>Could this be?</i>

37:59.683 --> 38:00.880
<i>No.</i>

38:02.147 --> 38:04.213
<i>Is that her?</i>

38:04.248 --> 38:05.654
<i>I think...</i>

38:05.689 --> 38:06.886
<i>think it is.</i>

38:27.073 --> 38:28.336
Excuse me, miss.

38:28.371 --> 38:30.041
You need a hand?

38:30.076 --> 38:31.306
-Oh...
<i>-It's not her.</i>

38:31.341 --> 38:32.879
No, thank you.

38:32.914 --> 38:35.684
My husband should be
right down, but thanks.

38:35.719 --> 38:37.389
<i>- Husband?</i>

38:37.424 --> 38:38.984
<i>Do I really come across</i>
<i>like a serial killer?</i>

38:39.019 --> 38:40.249
Are you sure?
I really don't mind.

38:40.284 --> 38:41.822
No, really, I'm okay.

38:41.857 --> 38:42.856
Thank you.

38:42.891 --> 38:44.429
Okay, okay.

38:44.464 --> 38:47.663
<i>Maybe I'll just</i>
<i>knock on the door.</i>

38:47.698 --> 38:49.093
Oh, shit.

38:50.261 --> 38:52.569
Oh, I'm...
I'm so sorry.

38:52.604 --> 38:54.263
You must be Tyler.

38:54.298 --> 38:56.705
And this is your Airbnb.

38:56.740 --> 38:57.838
Please forgive me.

38:57.873 --> 38:59.169
I thought that you were just-

38:59.204 --> 39:00.544
Don't worry about it.
It's okay.

39:00.579 --> 39:01.611
I just wanted to come by
and make sure

39:01.646 --> 39:03.107
you had everything you need.

39:03.142 --> 39:04.174
-That's all.
-Oh, I really appreciate it.

39:04.209 --> 39:05.340
Everything looks lovely.

39:05.375 --> 39:06.946
-Okay.
-Thank you.

39:06.981 --> 39:07.947
-Well, you enjoy your stay.
-Have a great day.

39:07.982 --> 39:09.751
-No problem.
-Thanks.

39:09.786 --> 39:10.851
-Don't forget your-
-Uh.

39:10.886 --> 39:11.951
There you go.

39:13.284 --> 39:14.723
<i>Looks like you got away from me.</i>

39:15.924 --> 39:18.254
<i>Probably for the best.</i>

39:18.289 --> 39:23.600
<i>Maybe I'll see you again,</i>
<i>but maybe I'm not supposed to.</i>

39:23.635 --> 39:26.933
<i>Besides, I have work to do.</i>

40:04.269 --> 40:08.007
<i>Is it wrong or is it right</i>
<i>for the right reasons?</i>

40:11.375 --> 40:14.046
<i>Either way, I could be wrong</i>
<i>for doing the right thing.</i>

40:16.556 --> 40:17.720
- Yeah.

40:46.476 --> 40:47.882
Oh, no!

40:54.088 --> 40:55.384
No!
Please don't!

40:55.419 --> 40:57.529
Please.

41:50.375 --> 41:51.880
- Hi.

41:51.915 --> 41:54.014
Liz, hey.

41:54.049 --> 41:55.114
You okay?

41:56.381 --> 41:58.689
Zach's having an affair.

41:58.724 --> 42:00.625
<i>And now you're here.</i>

42:00.660 --> 42:02.187
Liz, I'm sorry to hear that.

42:02.222 --> 42:03.958
I'm sorry I didn't come earlier.

42:05.093 --> 42:06.763
It's okay.
I totally-

42:11.165 --> 42:13.396
I'm sorry.
I'm so sorry about this.

42:35.321 --> 42:36.694
<i>This isn't what it looks like.</i>

42:39.358 --> 42:41.094
<i>I'm lying.</i>

42:41.129 --> 42:42.865
<i>This is exactly</i>
<i>what it looks like.</i>

42:44.495 --> 42:47.100
<i>This is my safe zone,</i>

42:47.135 --> 42:49.608
<i>because this leads</i>
<i>to absolutely nothing.</i>

42:51.304 --> 42:54.778
<i>Just a one-time thing</i>
<i>to ease a broken heart.</i>

42:56.815 --> 42:58.507
<i>I have a thing</i>
<i>for women in pain.</i>

42:59.818 --> 43:02.687
<i>And apparently,</i>
<i>they have a thing for me.</i>

43:04.856 --> 43:07.186
<i>It's obvious why.</i>

43:07.221 --> 43:09.122
<i>I make them feel safe.</i>

43:10.653 --> 43:13.632
<i>They tell me their darkest,</i>
<i>most intimate secrets</i>

43:15.130 --> 43:17.636
<i>because I listen, I'm trusted.</i>

43:20.168 --> 43:23.532
<i>Now they know,</i>
<i>they are living lives</i>

43:23.567 --> 43:24.973
<i>with their cheating spouses.</i>

43:38.516 --> 43:41.825
<i>Listen,</i>
<i>before you react</i>

43:41.860 --> 43:46.225
<i>and do the first thing</i>
<i>that comes to mind, think,</i>

43:46.260 --> 43:48.359
<i>what is the best way</i>
<i>in getting revenge?</i>

43:49.769 --> 43:52.033
<i>What will hurt him the most?</i>

43:52.068 --> 43:54.431
<i>This is what you do.</i>

43:56.204 --> 43:57.676
<i>I'm sorry for your pain.</i>

43:59.372 --> 44:02.076
<i>These files were only</i>
<i>for your eyes</i>

44:02.111 --> 44:06.982
<i>and will be deleted</i>
<i>in three, two, one.</i>

44:11.923 --> 44:13.186
I really messed up.

44:16.026 --> 44:17.762
I wish she'd give me
a second chance.

44:21.592 --> 44:25.198
Every day it hurts

44:25.233 --> 44:28.399
more and more,

44:29.633 --> 44:32.909
and you'd think that in time,

44:32.944 --> 44:36.748
the pain would heal,
but not this pain.

44:38.147 --> 44:40.477
She was the love of my life,
and now she's gone.

44:41.788 --> 44:42.952
She left me.

44:45.121 --> 44:46.318
I would have changed for her.

44:48.421 --> 44:49.728
Whatever she needed.

44:52.425 --> 44:53.622
If she'd just
come back to me,

44:53.657 --> 44:56.394
I could tell her, show her.

45:09.079 --> 45:12.245
It would have been
31 years today.

45:12.280 --> 45:14.478
Today.

45:14.513 --> 45:17.283
And I'm trying, man.

45:17.318 --> 45:20.583
It's just so, so hard,

45:22.455 --> 45:24.257
and I haven't even been
talking to our daughter

45:24.292 --> 45:25.654
since she left us and...

45:27.427 --> 45:30.769
They don't need me, we need her.

45:34.302 --> 45:36.533
There's just nothing left
for me here anymore.

45:51.682 --> 45:56.058
Harold,
Bethany didn't leave you.

45:57.963 --> 45:59.160
She passed away.

46:00.559 --> 46:01.998
Almost four years ago.

46:04.167 --> 46:05.364
She's not coming back.

46:06.697 --> 46:10.006
You don't think...
I know she's dead.

46:15.046 --> 46:16.639
If she could speak to you,

46:16.674 --> 46:18.014
I'm sure she would tell you
to find happiness.

46:19.380 --> 46:20.676
Yeah, she would.

46:24.319 --> 46:26.187
That's why I'm here.

46:26.222 --> 46:27.386
I'm trying.

46:29.588 --> 46:30.829
You're doing great.

46:33.691 --> 46:36.725
<i>- First sessions</i>
<i>are always the worst.</i>

46:36.760 --> 46:39.134
<i>It usually starts</i>
<i>as a competition about</i>

46:39.169 --> 46:41.202
<i>who's right and who's wrong,</i>

46:41.237 --> 46:44.667
<i>or like in this case,</i>
<i>we sit here in complete silence.</i>

46:44.702 --> 46:47.010
Why don't we begin with
what brought you two in today?

46:55.922 --> 46:56.921
He's cheating on me.

46:56.956 --> 46:58.186
No, I'm not.

46:58.221 --> 46:59.891
Yes, you are.
Just admit it.

46:59.926 --> 47:01.321
Why would I cheat on you?

47:01.356 --> 47:02.993
You tell me,
you're the one doing it.

47:03.028 --> 47:04.192
I love you.

47:04.227 --> 47:05.721
Don't touch me.

47:08.759 --> 47:11.826
Hilda, why are you saying
Johnathon is cheating on you?

47:11.861 --> 47:13.465
Because he is.

47:14.765 --> 47:15.830
I understand.

47:15.865 --> 47:18.404
I can just feel it.

47:18.439 --> 47:19.768
It's like a woman's intuition.

47:20.980 --> 47:23.178
Are there any other reasons?

47:23.213 --> 47:24.410
Because...

47:25.985 --> 47:27.512
we're not having sex,

47:27.547 --> 47:29.613
so I know
he's getting it from somewhere.

47:29.648 --> 47:31.549
Every time
I try to make a move,

47:31.584 --> 47:33.716
you turn me down.

47:33.751 --> 47:35.619
-You don't try.
-Well, not anymore.

47:35.654 --> 47:37.225
Why would I continue to try

47:37.260 --> 47:38.754
when all I get are your excuses?

