a little jealous, that's all.

1:06:47.145 --> 1:06:49.002
No, I'm... I'm just-

1:06:49.037 --> 1:06:50.344
I'm not jealous,
I'm just curious.

1:06:50.379 --> 1:06:52.511
So tell me about her.

1:06:52.546 --> 1:06:54.414
We went on a date

1:06:56.044 --> 1:06:57.846
and I haven't heard from her.

1:06:57.881 --> 1:07:00.222
But isn't that what you prefer,
to keep things simple,

1:07:00.257 --> 1:07:02.224
keep your urges in check?

1:07:02.259 --> 1:07:03.918
Yeah, it is.

1:07:05.790 --> 1:07:07.625
I just kind of want to see
her again, you know?

1:07:07.660 --> 1:07:08.956
So then why don't you call her?

1:07:10.135 --> 1:07:11.332
I don't have her number.

1:07:12.500 --> 1:07:14.500
Okay, so question, uh,

1:07:15.998 --> 1:07:18.867
what is it about her that makes
you want to see her again?

1:07:18.902 --> 1:07:20.638
I don't know.

1:07:20.673 --> 1:07:22.310
Well, maybe you should
ask yourself why.

1:07:27.515 --> 1:07:29.075
Mmm.

1:07:29.110 --> 1:07:30.912
Hey, boss.

1:07:30.947 --> 1:07:32.650
You gotta try these cupcakes
Melissa made.

1:07:32.685 --> 1:07:35.290
Cupcakes, this early?

1:07:35.325 --> 1:07:38.326
-Mm-hmm.
-Yeah, you should try one.

1:07:38.361 --> 1:07:39.921
I thought
you was allergic to chocolate.

1:07:39.956 --> 1:07:41.395
Mmm, I am.

1:07:41.430 --> 1:07:42.792
It's just food coloring.

1:07:42.827 --> 1:07:44.893
No, it isn't.

1:07:44.928 --> 1:07:46.169
Stop playing.

1:07:46.204 --> 1:07:47.962
Why would I dye
a vanilla cupcake

1:07:47.997 --> 1:07:49.502
to look like
a chocolate cupcake?

1:08:00.383 --> 1:08:03.109
Um, Melissa, listen,
I'm sorry about-

1:08:03.144 --> 1:08:05.353
I'm so sorry.

1:08:05.388 --> 1:08:06.684
I don't know
what I was thinking.

1:08:08.193 --> 1:08:09.819
I hope I didn't make
you uncomfortable

1:08:09.854 --> 1:08:11.161
or anything like that.

1:08:11.196 --> 1:08:13.020
No, you didn't.

1:08:13.055 --> 1:08:15.627
The last thing I want to do
is ruin our work environment.

1:08:15.662 --> 1:08:16.958
Yeah, me too.

1:08:18.159 --> 1:08:20.203
I apologize, too.

1:08:20.238 --> 1:08:21.699
I should've known better

1:08:21.734 --> 1:08:24.636
when we had
our first little encounter.

1:08:24.671 --> 1:08:26.275
Mm-hmm.

1:08:26.310 --> 1:08:27.705
But I want you to know
I'm a professional.

1:08:27.740 --> 1:08:29.003
I take my job very serious.

1:08:29.038 --> 1:08:30.213
I don't want you to think I'm-

1:08:30.248 --> 1:08:31.379
I know that.

1:08:32.844 --> 1:08:34.217
I was just being jealous.

1:08:36.045 --> 1:08:37.484
I think you're a great guy.

1:08:41.017 --> 1:08:42.324
Um, ignore what I said.

1:08:43.921 --> 1:08:45.492
So we good?

1:08:45.527 --> 1:08:46.526
Guys, I think
I need to go to the hospital.

1:08:46.561 --> 1:08:48.022
-Damn!
-Oh, my God!

1:08:54.162 --> 1:08:56.338
He'll be okay.

1:08:56.373 --> 1:08:57.438
I'll cover for him.

1:08:59.739 --> 1:09:01.541
Uh, are you sure?

1:09:01.576 --> 1:09:02.905
-I don't want to-
-Yeah.

1:09:02.940 --> 1:09:04.643
Okay...
overwhelm you or anything.

1:09:04.678 --> 1:09:06.139
Not a problem...

1:09:06.174 --> 1:09:07.679
Okay.

1:09:07.714 --> 1:09:08.845
..boss.

1:09:23.301 --> 1:09:25.367
<i>Today is going</i>
<i>to be one of those days.</i>

1:09:39.779 --> 1:09:41.383
<i>What have you been up to?</i>

1:09:43.145 --> 1:09:46.113
<i>Maybe I should</i>
<i>send another message.</i>

1:09:46.148 --> 1:09:50.392
<i>Just to say thank you,</i>
<i>or maybe I should just ask...</i>

1:09:52.220 --> 1:09:53.494
<i>how are you.</i>

1:09:57.995 --> 1:09:59.764
<i>- Malcolm,</i>
<i>your 9 o'clock is here.</i>

1:10:02.769 --> 1:10:04.164
How does that make you feel?

1:10:05.838 --> 1:10:07.277
Angry.

1:10:07.312 --> 1:10:08.740
You want a clean sponge
and dirty dishes?

1:10:08.775 --> 1:10:10.808
My girl is driving me
fucking nuts.

1:10:10.843 --> 1:10:12.579
I don't really
wanna talk about it.

1:10:12.614 --> 1:10:14.075
I don't know what to do anymore.

1:10:14.110 --> 1:10:16.418
You're at home all day
while I'm working.

1:10:16.453 --> 1:10:17.881
Man, it's not even like

1:10:17.916 --> 1:10:20.752
something specific or,
like, her.

1:10:20.787 --> 1:10:24.217
Just...
just every day, bro, with her.

1:10:24.252 --> 1:10:28.562
Without someone being
there to actually

1:10:28.597 --> 1:10:31.598
speak for our people,
then we have no voice.

1:10:31.633 --> 1:10:33.633
We become complacent
like we have now.

1:10:33.668 --> 1:10:36.097
But what about you?

1:10:36.132 --> 1:10:37.637
What about, what about me?

1:10:37.672 --> 1:10:39.232
I'm at home, I'm at the crib.

1:10:39.267 --> 1:10:41.443
You know where
I'm at all the time.

1:10:41.478 --> 1:10:42.840
I need... I need a man.

1:10:42.875 --> 1:10:44.347
Is that, is that what
you're saying?

1:10:44.382 --> 1:10:45.645
I clean up the place,
I put it all back.

1:10:45.680 --> 1:10:47.009
She says nothing.

1:10:47.044 --> 1:10:48.780
-I want this to-
-Nothing's happening.

1:10:48.815 --> 1:10:50.485
I'm not going to stop
playing my game.

1:10:50.520 --> 1:10:51.948
I'm not going to stop
loving you.

1:10:51.983 --> 1:10:53.752
I can't take this shit anymore.

1:10:53.787 --> 1:10:56.920
I have this dream of me
getting on top of her, man.

1:10:56.955 --> 1:10:58.427
And it's not enough.

1:10:58.462 --> 1:10:59.791
We deserve more.

1:10:59.826 --> 1:11:01.826
I try to go out of my way
to make sure

1:11:01.861 --> 1:11:03.289
you feel comfortable,

1:11:03.324 --> 1:11:05.093
that you always have
your latest games.

1:11:05.128 --> 1:11:06.666
Are you married?

1:11:06.701 --> 1:11:08.030
Hmm.

1:11:08.065 --> 1:11:09.834
Am I wrong, though?
Like...

1:11:09.869 --> 1:11:11.341
She cheated on me with a guy.

1:11:11.376 --> 1:11:13.343
I need someone
to be there for me.

1:11:13.378 --> 1:11:14.608
Am I overreacting?

1:11:14.643 --> 1:11:15.807
Oh, we'll see.

1:11:15.842 --> 1:11:16.973
All right, bro.

1:11:17.008 --> 1:11:18.139
-Thanks.
-Thank you.

1:11:18.174 --> 1:11:19.382
Appreciate it.

1:11:28.184 --> 1:11:29.359
How are you holding up?

1:11:30.527 --> 1:11:31.889
I'm hanging.

1:11:31.924 --> 1:11:33.220
How's Kevin?

1:11:33.255 --> 1:11:35.695
He's okay.
He's at the doctor, so...

1:11:35.730 --> 1:11:37.730
Okay, good.

1:11:37.765 --> 1:11:39.094
You ready for your
last appointment?

1:11:40.328 --> 1:11:41.503
Yeah, no choice.

1:11:42.704 --> 1:11:44.638
Yeah, let's get it done.

1:11:44.673 --> 1:11:45.837
You got it.

1:11:47.709 --> 1:11:49.005
Oh, Melissa.

1:11:51.581 --> 1:11:52.778
Thank you.

1:12:18.773 --> 1:12:20.201
I'm sorry about this.

1:12:20.236 --> 1:12:21.840
I had an accident.

1:12:21.875 --> 1:12:23.237
Oh, no worries.

1:12:26.814 --> 1:12:28.011
<i>Shit.</i>

1:12:28.046 --> 1:12:30.046
Malcolm, is it?

1:12:30.081 --> 1:12:31.487
It is.

1:12:33.381 --> 1:12:34.424
Veronica, right?

1:12:34.459 --> 1:12:36.382
Yes, it is.

1:12:36.417 --> 1:12:38.791
-Nice to meet you.
-Nice to meet you.

1:12:38.826 --> 1:12:40.463
Please take a seat.

1:12:42.467 --> 1:12:43.730
<i>Why are you here?</i>

1:12:45.965 --> 1:12:47.228
<i>You figured it out?</i>

1:12:48.396 --> 1:12:49.472
Damn.

1:12:49.507 --> 1:12:51.199
Okay.

1:12:51.234 --> 1:12:52.442
Sorry about that,

1:12:54.237 --> 1:12:56.270
I had a little accident
a minute ago.

1:13:02.113 --> 1:13:05.983
So, what brings you in?

1:13:06.018 --> 1:13:08.414
Oh, you just get right to it?

1:13:08.449 --> 1:13:09.756
-Okay.
-Um...

1:13:09.791 --> 1:13:11.219
I'm sorry about that.

1:13:11.254 --> 1:13:12.319
How's your day?

1:13:12.354 --> 1:13:14.387
<i>I'm completely fucking up.</i>

1:13:14.422 --> 1:13:15.663
Malcolm.

1:13:16.831 --> 1:13:17.962
Yes.

1:13:17.997 --> 1:13:19.425
<i>Why are you messing with me?</i>

1:13:19.460 --> 1:13:21.064
<i>Just come out and say it.</i>

1:13:21.099 --> 1:13:23.363
Is it okay if I ask you
some questions first?

1:13:24.773 --> 1:13:26.135
Of course.

1:13:26.170 --> 1:13:27.675
It's just my first time
doing this,

1:13:27.710 --> 1:13:29.237
and I feel it'll help me...

1:13:29.272 --> 1:13:30.579
Open up.

1:13:30.614 --> 1:13:32.845
I understand.

1:13:32.880 --> 1:13:34.583
What would you like to know?

1:13:34.618 --> 1:13:36.178
How long have
you been doing this?

1:13:38.446 --> 1:13:40.116
Almost a year.

1:13:40.151 --> 1:13:41.381
Hmm.

1:13:43.385 --> 1:13:45.792
What made you want to do this?

1:13:45.827 --> 1:13:48.861
People hurting people.

1:13:51.866 --> 1:13:54.031
You can give a person
everything and...

1:13:56.233 --> 1:13:58.332
get nothing,
but pain every time.

1:13:58.367 --> 1:14:00.367
You're talking from experience?

1:14:02.008 --> 1:14:05.174
Tell me about your experiences.

1:14:07.046 --> 1:14:09.442
Talking about relationships?

1:14:09.477 --> 1:14:10.982
Talking about...

1:14:12.887 --> 1:14:14.524
whatever the question
means to you.

1:14:16.825 --> 1:14:19.056
We're here to talk
about you, not me.

1:14:21.665 --> 1:14:23.027
Next question.

1:14:25.669 --> 1:14:28.065
What's this?

1:14:28.100 --> 1:14:29.902
The infinity symbol.

1:14:29.937 --> 1:14:33.939
I know,
but there's a piece missing.

1:14:35.437 --> 1:14:36.711
It's broken.

1:14:38.209 --> 1:14:41.782
When a spouse cheats,
they're breaking vows.

1:14:44.622 --> 1:14:46.413
Tell me something about you.

1:14:46.448 --> 1:14:47.920
In time.

1:14:51.189 --> 1:14:52.760
Are you married?

1:14:52.795 --> 1:14:55.598
I am single, actually.

1:14:55.633 --> 1:14:57.259
You?

1:14:57.294 --> 1:15:00.097
But you do couples therapy.

1:15:00.132 --> 1:15:02.264
I do.

1:15:02.299 --> 1:15:03.771
Do I need to be
in a relationship

1:15:03.806 --> 1:15:05.707
to do couples therapy?

1:15:05.742 --> 1:15:06.873
No.

1:15:06.908 --> 1:15:08.006
I'm sorry.

1:15:08.041 --> 1:15:10.679
Yeah, I'm single, at the moment.

1:15:10.714 --> 1:15:11.944
At the moment.

1:15:13.277 --> 1:15:15.541
So that means
there's someone,

1:15:15.576 --> 1:15:17.378
you're just not sure
how serious it is.

1:15:18.755 --> 1:15:20.414
It's complicated.

1:15:20.449 --> 1:15:21.756
It's always complicated.

1:15:23.221 --> 1:15:24.627
But not with you.

1:15:26.455 --> 1:15:27.729
What do you mean?

1:15:27.764 --> 1:15:29.599
I see you embedded this.

1:15:30.899 --> 1:15:32.426
Why?

1:15:32.461 --> 1:15:33.900
Because you gave it to me.

1:15:37.939 --> 1:15:39.235
Tell me.

1:15:40.469 --> 1:15:42.238
Do you ever think about
that night?

1:15:45.683 --> 1:15:48.277
Uh, thank you,
I think that's everything.

1:15:53.317 --> 1:15:54.756
Maybe we can...

1:15:55.957 --> 1:15:58.221
do this again sometime?

1:15:58.256 --> 1:15:59.354
Maybe.

1:16:09.597 --> 1:16:11.432
Does she make
you dinner every night?

1:16:14.811 --> 1:16:16.008
Most nights.

1:16:17.814 --> 1:16:20.342
Does she take care of the kids,
keep the house clean?

1:16:23.820 --> 1:16:25.017
Yeah.

1:16:26.647 --> 1:16:27.789
Do you?

1:16:31.289 --> 1:16:32.662
I mean, I have work.

1:16:34.127 --> 1:16:35.357
Does she work?

1:16:40.298 --> 1:16:41.462
Yeah.

1:16:42.971 --> 1:16:44.905
So she loves you.

1:16:46.337 --> 1:16:47.941
Look, just because
people have been together

1:16:47.976 --> 1:16:49.943
for a long time,
it doesn't mean

1:16:49.978 --> 1:16:52.341
the romance
or affection has died.

1:16:52.376 --> 1:16:54.882
It just changes.

1:16:54.917 --> 1:16:57.720
I mean, what do
you want from her?

1:17:00.351 --> 1:17:01.988
Want her to bring you
flowers every day.

1:17:03.519 --> 1:17:04.991
Do you bring her flowers?

1:17:08.898 --> 1:17:10.799
So, maybe she's feeling

1:17:10.834 --> 1:17:12.493
some of what you're feeling
right now.

1:17:14.530 --> 1:17:17.366
And you said you've tried
everything, I mean, have you?

1:17:17.401 --> 1:17:21.843
If you simply just tried
to sit down and talk with her,

1:17:21.878 --> 1:17:25.506
communicate how you feel
and why you feel this way,

1:17:25.541 --> 1:17:28.850
and then ask her how she feels.

1:17:32.790 --> 1:17:34.581
You ever thought about
being a therapist?

1:17:38.686 --> 1:17:39.861
What up, boss?

1:17:39.896 --> 1:17:40.961
You ready
for your 2 o'clock?

1:17:42.525 --> 1:17:46.164
Kevin, has a Veronica Wilson
called in,

1:17:46.199 --> 1:17:47.737
to make her next appointment?

1:17:47.772 --> 1:17:49.530
She still hasn't,
but I'll be sure to let you know

1:17:49.565 --> 1:17:51.598
when she does, I got you.

1:17:51.633 --> 1:17:52.742
Damn.

1:17:52.777 --> 1:17:53.941
Oh, matter of fact, you know

1:17:53.976 --> 1:17:55.404
her number's on the file, right?

1:17:55.439 --> 1:17:56.537
I'm just saying.

1:17:57.705 --> 1:17:59.881
I know.

1:17:59.916 --> 1:18:02.345
But what do I always tell you?

1:18:02.380 --> 1:18:03.918
Not to eat chocolate
at work again.

1:18:03.953 --> 1:18:06.349
If I want to kill myself,
do it on my own time.

1:18:06.384 --> 1:18:07.581
The other thing.

1:18:09.387 --> 1:18:10.727
To be patient.

1:18:14.260 --> 1:18:15.655
I'm letting her come to me.

1:18:38.647 --> 1:18:40.152
<i>Why did you come here?</i>

1:18:42.288 --> 1:18:43.991
<i>If I have to be honest,</i>

1:18:44.026 --> 1:18:46.026
<i>I didn't think it would take you</i>
<i>this long to come back.</i>

1:18:49.427 --> 1:18:50.591
Hey.

1:18:50.626 --> 1:18:51.933
Hey, hey.

1:18:51.968 --> 1:18:53.099
I hope you don't mind.

1:18:53.134 --> 1:18:54.661
The door was open and I just...

1:18:54.696 --> 1:18:56.168
Excuse me, miss,
what's your name?

1:18:56.203 --> 1:18:57.598
Veronica.

1:18:57.633 --> 1:18:58.973
Veronica.

1:18:59.008 --> 1:19:01.008
Yes, Veronica Wilson.

1:19:01.043 --> 1:19:02.141
-I had an appointment.
-Yeah.

1:19:02.176 --> 1:19:03.571
You called yesterday,

1:19:03.606 --> 1:19:05.144
but your phone was like
a little static.

1:19:05.179 --> 1:19:05.947
What you got,
a little android or something?

1:19:05.982 --> 1:19:07.740
Thank you, Kevin.

1:19:07.775 --> 1:19:09.148
Okay.

1:19:09.183 --> 1:19:10.347
Um, do y'all need anything?

1:19:10.382 --> 1:19:12.019
-I'm fine.
-You sure?

1:19:12.054 --> 1:19:13.119
I'll be right out here
if you do.

1:19:13.154 --> 1:19:15.187
Kevin, close the door.

1:19:15.222 --> 1:19:16.892
Well, I'm gonna do some
paperwork or something.

1:19:19.490 --> 1:19:20.720
Did you tell him about me?

1:19:22.691 --> 1:19:26.396
Uh, did I...

1:19:29.907 --> 1:19:31.203
Please, take a seat.

1:19:37.981 --> 1:19:39.640
I'm glad you decided
to come back.

1:19:40.885 --> 1:19:42.148
Can I ask you a question?

1:19:42.183 --> 1:19:44.315
More questions?

1:19:44.350 --> 1:19:46.350
I know.

1:19:46.385 --> 1:19:47.516
You know,
you're not paying me

1:19:47.551 --> 1:19:49.452
to learn about me.

1:19:49.487 --> 1:19:50.585
<i>Or are you?</i>

1:19:55.196 --> 1:19:57.724
I was just wondering
if it's at all possible

1:19:57.759 --> 1:19:59.594
to have sessions elsewhere.

1:20:00.696 --> 1:20:02.399
Elsewhere?

1:20:02.434 --> 1:20:03.873
I know that's unprofessional.

1:20:03.908 --> 1:20:06.469
I just think that
a different environment

1:20:06.504 --> 1:20:08.606
might help me
communicate better.

1:20:11.674 --> 1:20:12.739
I understand.

1:20:15.051 --> 1:20:16.215
I know a place.

1:20:19.748 --> 1:20:20.956
Is this better?

1:20:22.421 --> 1:20:23.585
Much better.

1:20:24.786 --> 1:20:28.359
You know, I'm the same way.

1:20:28.394 --> 1:20:30.262
What do you mean?

1:20:30.297 --> 1:20:32.935
How about just this
once we talk about you?

1:20:34.763 --> 1:20:36.367
Well, I appreciate
what you're doing.

1:20:37.535 --> 1:20:38.864
It definitely helps.

1:20:38.899 --> 1:20:40.107
Yeah.

1:20:43.574 --> 1:20:44.771
I have an idea.

1:20:46.412 --> 1:20:49.281
Instead of these being like
typical therapy sessions,

1:20:50.746 --> 1:20:52.053
why don't we be friends?

1:20:53.782 --> 1:20:55.958
What do you mean, friends?

1:20:55.993 --> 1:20:58.026
I mean, instead of us
meeting at my office

1:20:58.061 --> 1:21:00.963
once a week,
we can meet at other places.

1:21:03.099 --> 1:21:04.395
Like dating?

1:21:06.135 --> 1:21:08.003
Uh, no, not like dating.

1:21:09.798 --> 1:21:11.501
Just until you feel comfortable.

1:21:15.639 --> 1:21:17.177
I'll choose the next place.

1:21:40.631 --> 1:21:42.103
Okay, okay, okay.

1:21:42.138 --> 1:21:43.335
Okay.

1:21:43.370 --> 1:21:44.699
You okay?

1:21:46.109 --> 1:21:47.933
I can't believe I agreed to it.

1:21:47.968 --> 1:21:49.638
What were you expecting?

1:21:49.673 --> 1:21:51.409
Dinner and movie?

1:21:51.444 --> 1:21:52.575
Maybe.

1:22:10.133 --> 1:22:11.330
